title: ERROR: invalid page header in block
description: PostgreSQL detected corruption in a data page header, indicating potential disk or memory corruption.
common_causes: Hardware failure, disk corruption, memory errors, improper shutdown, file system issues.
resolution:
- Run file system check: `fsck` on affected partition.
- Check hardware health: disk SMART status and memory tests.
- Restore from backup if corruption is extensive.
- Use pg_resetwal cautiously for WAL corruption.
- Consider zero_damaged_pages = on as temporary measure (data loss risk).
